Simulate the business process of a user buying toothpaste:

1. Show the best selling toothpaste in the past week (Data Virtualization)

2. List toothpaste related products, razors, towels, facial cleansers (Data propagation)

3. Users buy toothpaste, the inventory is reduced accordingly, this toothpaste popularity +1 (Changed Data Capture)

4. The stock of toothpaste is not enough and needs to be restocked, but the toothpaste supplier is also out of stock, 
	 Adjust all systems to immediately remove this toothpaste and close the advertisement of this toothpaste (Data federation)

5. The supervisor reanalyzed the sales of this toothpaste and worked out a new purchase plan (Data consolidation)

